      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with dreams and actual life in them—died a long time ago. now im just... a shell. just a walking corpse going through the motions of a life i dont even belong to anymore.",
